{
  "name": "PAN NGFW - Allowlist - Add to EDL Exception List",
  "description": "Adds an exception entry (IP, domain, or URL) to a specified External Dynamic List (EDL) on a PAN NGFW firewall, then commits the configuration. Use this to allowlist an indicator that would otherwise be blocked by an EDL-based security policy.",
